data.description: Welcome to modern living in this stunning 4-bedroom, 3.5-bath contemporary townhome built in 2021. The thoughtful design features hardwood floors on the entrance and main living levels, creating a seamless flow throughout. The heart of the home, the kitchen, boasts a large island, quartz countertops, and stainless steel appliances, perfect for culinary enthusiasts. The open concept on the main living area allows for flow from the kitchen to the dining area and familyroom.  From the dining area, step out onto the spacious balcony facing lush trees, providing a serene escape right at home.  Natural light floods the space through large windows, illuminating the elegant details of the contemporary architecture. The upper floor hosts the convenience of a laundry room, making daily chores a breeze. In addition,  you will find the primary bedroom with large walk-in closet, and ensuite bath.  The primary bath features a dual double sink granite vanity, custom tile shower with bench and separate water closet.  There are two additional bedrooms and a full bath on this level as well.  The fourth bedroom and full bath can be found on the entrance level of the home.  The attached 2-car garage adds both convenience and security.  North Quarter offers community green spaces, tot lots and proximity to all North Bethesda has to offer.  Nestled off of Randolph Rd and within minutes to Pike and Rose, enjoy the vibrant lifestyle with shopping and dining options just moments away. Plus, easy access to major commuter routes enhances the appeal of this modern oasis.
